    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于SAVE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一名前特种部队特工，也是USTC（UDT / SEAL Tactical Consulting）的成员，这是一家专门从事安保服务的韩国私营军事公司。 有一天，来自米斯卡顿大学的教授给你一笔不可抗拒的钱，以换取可疑的任务 - 追踪由名为SENARA福音传教团（SENARA Gospel Mission）的宗教团体拥有的6000吨客轮&quot;SENARA&quot;的航行，并监测船上任何仪式活动的迹象。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了完成本合同，您和您的团队必须潜入&quot;SENARA&quot;，调查和收集客户要求的可疑证据 - 然而，该船隐藏着意想不到的超自然事件和潜伏在阴影中的隐患。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123290/extras/b50e1d288551e262343e55c06a8d696a.avif?t=1746584181\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123290/extras_big/b50e1d288551e262343e55c06a8d696a.avif?t=1746584181 width=800 height=458 /></span>在6000吨级船舶上精心重建的环境中体验现实的恐怖。 面对未知的威胁，为生存而战，将你的勇气和智慧置于终极考验。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123290/extras/365a502847ee20473cedb12eadb59289.avif?t=1746584181\" width=616 height=345 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >作战计划书 - “新国家号”船舰搜索作战任务概要</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这艘6000吨级的&quot;SENARA&quot;号船位于国际水域。 团队多达四名特工渗透到船上，并从战略上管理船上遇到的任何潜在威胁。 收集目标物品后，利用船上的救生艇逃生。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123290/extras/b3e4be2dd9b50c3352c764bc6ae0dbe2.poster.avif?t=1746584181\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123290/extras/b3e4be2dd9b50c3352c764bc6ae0dbe2.webm?t=1746584181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123290/extras/b3e4be2dd9b50c3352c764bc6ae0dbe2.mp4?t=1746584181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第1阶段 - 搜索准备</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用大本营提供的资金为特派团做准备。 分配个人角色，并收集必要的设备，为搜索任务做准备。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123290/extras/29192d146a3c18ab37acb74951dbb441.poster.avif?t=1746584181\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123290/extras/29192d146a3c18ab37acb74951dbb441.webm?t=1746584181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123290/extras/29192d146a3c18ab37acb74951dbb441.mp4?t=1746584181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第2阶段 - 搜索</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参与作战的各要员需暗中潜入到不同位置，以防止受到内部反抗势力的干扰。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潜入后立即展开船舰搜索，并利用通信设备保持密切联系，尽可能多地对大量区域进行战略性搜索。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123290/extras/71a18de40ed1bf6d42fdbb7662263c9a.poster.avif?t=1746584181\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123290/extras/71a18de40ed1bf6d42fdbb7662263c9a.webm?t=1746584181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123290/extras/71a18de40ed1bf6d42fdbb7662263c9a.mp4?t=1746584181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第3阶段 - 应对威胁</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在执行船舰搜索任务时，需要迅速掌握船上可能存在的威胁要素，并在发现后立即公布，以便其他要员能够及时做出应对。搜索作战一旦被暴露，要员有极大可能会受到追踪与威胁，以此务必谨慎移动和探索，率先发现威胁并做出应对。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123290/extras/113d1a19049bf95f3c520003bda19e74.poster.avif?t=1746584181\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123290/extras/113d1a19049bf95f3c520003bda19e74.webm?t=1746584181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123290/extras/113d1a19049bf95f3c520003bda19e74.mp4?t=1746584181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第4阶段 - 收集目标物</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此次行动的主要目的是识别并回收指定目标物，并尽量获取隐藏在船上的贵重金属。同时，通过获取并使用执行任务所需的生存物品，来协助搜索任务的完成。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123290/extras/df177579ea94f93a26793d36eb8c9d8a.poster.avif?t=1746584181\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123290/extras/df177579ea94f93a26793d36eb8c9d8a.webm?t=1746584181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123290/extras/df177579ea94f93a26793d36eb8c9d8a.mp4?t=1746584181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第5阶段 - 逃离</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >确保目标物品后，请按照作战计划使用预定的撤离方式安全离开SENARA，以成功完成任务。</p>",
